<h1 class="title">Thank you so much for using GMR</h1>
<hr>
<p>Here at GMR we respect and appreciate every mathematician which enters the site. Thats why we care about the experience you have on this site.
We understand bugs can happen every now and again so if you see something you think isn't quite right please use this page to inform us of the bug.
If you have something else you want to talk to us about please share your thoughts using the contact form or details below. For those of you which
simply love the site we have a paypal link where you can donate directly to us. This helps us improve the site and provide even more GMR specific original
resources.</p>

<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-12">
      <h4>Message us directly</h4>
      <hr>
      <%= form_with(url: "/home/thank_you", method: "post", local: true) do |form| %>
      <div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <%=form.label :name%>
          <%= form.text_field :name, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Enter Name"%>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <%=form.label :email%>
          <%= form.text_field :email, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Enter email"%>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <%=form.label :message%>
          <%= form.text_area :message, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Type Enquiry here"%>
        </div>
      <%= form.submit "Send", class: "btn btn-outline-custom", id: "send-button"%>
      </div>
      <%end%>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-12">
      <div class='contact_details'>
        <h4>Contact details</h4>
        <hr>
        <h5>Send us an email at:</h5>
        <h5><i class="far fa-envelope"></i> - gcsemathsresources.co.uk@gmail.com </h5>
        <h5>Call our office during our open times:</h5>
        <h5><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> - 07471 479813 </h5>
      </div>
      <h4>Donate</h4>
      <hr>
      <p>Thank you so much for spending your valuable time on our website. We appreciate every second spent on this page. Unfortunately developing websites takes time and resources which are not free.
      If you are able to and believe that GMR is a genuinely useful tool please donate using the donate tool below. It is completed through paypal and is 100% secure. We will send a personalised thank you email to any
      donor.</p>
      <div class="donatebutton">
        <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top">
        <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick" />
        <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="RJTHQEDJVGQWG" />
        <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/GB/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" title="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!" alt="Donate with PayPal button" />
        <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypal.com/en_GB/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1" />
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
